<s> First, for those who were not at the Dublin meeting (I was not, but Roy was, and he has described it to me), the homepage of the meeting is available at: According to Roy, the meeting was held in Dublin, Ohio, where it was "damn cold." :-) It was organized by Stu Weivel of OCLC, and the project has a definite digital library influence.  </s>
