<s> You might think that 'lock discovery' is also a metadata issue, but it's a peculiar one, because it's transient, and has less to do with the resource than with the manager that supports the resource.  </s>
<s> For example, a cached entity shouldn't become invalidated just because the lock state of the resource it was derived from changes.  </s>
